data.description: Discover modern elegance in this pristine 4-bed, 3-bath home that feels brand new. It boasts a luxury "glam area" in the main bathroom, spacious living areas, and upgraded features throughout. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the stylish kitchen, perfect for entertaining. Upstairs, envision a versatile area that can serve as a game room, gym, or a media retreat based on your desires. Don't overlook the backyard oasis, featuring a spacious area designed for both relaxation & entertaining.
